{"content": "<p>Navaneeth Kishor captures the natural beauty encountered on his adventures through India. Navene's travel diary is an OpenSea collection titled <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/my-best-travel-diary\">'My Travel Diary</a>' and puts you right there with Navene, in places you'd rarely discover on your own. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unnamed-116.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/12/unnamed-116.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/12/unnamed-116.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/12/unnamed-116.jpg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2021/12/unnamed-116.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/63620440226056400879759004548323237382896873170392364189325409216282553745409\">Camels of Nubra Valley</a> by Navaneeth on OpenSea marketplace</figcaption></figure><blockquote>'These are some of my finest images of landscapes. The stories in each photographs entail thousands of miles travelling, days and weeks of planning, trekking, failures and hardships' says Navaneeth. </blockquote><p><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/63620440226056400879759004548323237382896873170392364189325409220680600256513\">Yellapetty Top</a> is an hour's walk from the nearest car friendly road, the ocean like waves of <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/63620440226056400879759004548323237382896873170392364189325409217382065373185\">Thar Desert</a> are otherworldly and then there's the <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/63620440226056400879759004548323237382896873170392364189325409216282553745409\">Camels of Nubra Valley</a>. The sense of travelling through foreigns lands is encapsulated best by Camels of Nubra Valley. A trio of camels and their riders are led by a fourth capped man purposefully walking across a shadowed horizon. The distant mountains conveying the scale of the journey. <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@navaneethkishor/~/59436\">The Eternal Sail</a> is Navene's first mint on Foundation and also conveys a grand journey, this time over water.</p><p><em>\"I love to capture the very essence of a life moment, entwined with a story.\" says Navaneeth.</em></p><p>Navaneeth grew up near a large majestic mountain called <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/63620440226056400879759004548323237382896873170392364189325409219581088628737\">Illikkal Kallu</a> and heard stories about the local heroes who climbed to the top. </p><blockquote>\"The farthest destination I once imagined has now become my nearest location. I've logged thousands of kilometers now. But the place that fascinated me to travel as a child has always been my favourite.\" says Navaneeth.</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unnamed-117.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/12/unnamed-117.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/12/unnamed-117.jpg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/12/unnamed-117.jpg 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w2400/2021/12/unnamed-117.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/63620440226056400879759004548323237382896873170392364189325409219581088628737\">The Majestic Illikkal Kallu</a> by Navaneeth on OpenSea marketplace</figcaption></figure><p>Natural beauty isn't the main event of Navaneeth's photographic story making, it's simply what he uses to paint lens based stories with personal meaning.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-06-at-9.53.00-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1846\" height=\"962\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-06-at-9.53.00-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-06-at-9.53.00-AM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-06-at-9.53.00-AM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Screen-Shot-2021-12-06-at-9.53.00-AM.png 1846w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"></figure><blockquote>Get up in the morning.<br />Put your shoes on.<br />Take a hike up the hills.<br />Make Your Happiest Jump Ever.</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">A collection of ten 1/1 photographs of the most incredible destinations I encountered during my journey through India. Personal favorites, hand-picked by myself.<a href=\"https://t.co/r2fnqqtm8M\">https://t.co/r2fnqqtm8M</a><br /><br />Five are listed now!  Thank you all <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NFTDrop?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NFTDrop</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nftcollector?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#nftcollector</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nftphotography?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#nftphotography</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/gzHoHVbJXl\">pic.twitter.com/gzHoHVbJXl</a></p>&mdash; Navane.ΞTH (@navaneeth_kish) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/navaneeth_kish/status/1441258490211696649?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">September 24, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>Follow <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@navaneethkishor\">Navaneeth Kishor's art on Foundation</a> or share in the joy of his <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/my-best-travel-diary\">travel diary on OpenSea</a>.</p><p></p><hr /><p>Receive new artist features by email.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-left\"><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Subscribe to MintFace</a></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-pink\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">💡</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><strong>Artists. Join the next <a href=\"https://maven.com/mintface/nft-digital-artist-economy\">Digital Artist Economy Accelerator</a> </strong>and launch your NFT collection with confidence on your own smart contract.</div></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-purple\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">💡</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><strong>Collectors. </strong><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\">Subscribe to MintFace Premium</a> for $USD9 per month. MintFace surfaces great artists and artworks so you don't have to.</div></div><p></p>"}